<div class="app-drawer-wrapper" {{did-insert this.start}}>
    <div class="drawer-nav-btn">
        <button type="button" class="hamburger hamburger--elastic is-active">
            <span class="hamburger-box"><span class="hamburger-inner"></span></span>
        </button>
    </div>
    <div class="drawer-content-wrapper">
        <div id="drawer-scrollbar-container" class="scrollbar-container">
            <h3 class="drawer-heading">Utility</h3>
            {{!-- men√π di navigazione --}}
            <div class="card-header">
                <ul class="nav nav-justified">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-drawer-0" id="to-tab-drawer-0" class="active nav-link">Traduzioni</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-drawer-1" class="nav-link">Tab 2</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a data-toggle="tab" href="#tab-drawer-2" class="nav-link">Tab 3</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="tab-content">
                {{!-- contenuto tab traduzioni --}}
                <div class="tab-pane active" id="tab-drawer-0" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="drawer-section">
                        <p>Se attivi il servizio, tutti i testi inseriti con il componente di traduzione mostreranno un'icona di modifica, che consente di modificare il testo nella lingua corrente.</p>
                        <ul class="list-group mb-3">
                            <li class="list-group-item">
                                <div class="widget-content p-0">
                                    <div class="widget-content-wrapper">
                                        <div class="widget-content-left mr-3">
                                            <input class="form-check-input drawer-lang-translation" type="checkbox" data-toggle="toggle" data-onstyle="success">
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="widget-content-left">
                                            <div class="widget-heading">Traduzione</div>
                                            <div class="widget-subheading">Attiva la traduzione on-the-fly</div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div id="edit-translation-area" style="display: none;">
                        <h3 class="drawer-heading">
                            Modifica testo
                        </h3>
                        <div class="drawer-section">
                            <form>
                                <div class="form-row">
                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                        <div class="position-relative form-group">
                                            <label for="change-translation-app" class="">Chiave</label>
                                            <input type="text" id="change-translation-key" class="form-control" disabled />
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                        <div class="position-relative form-group">
                                            <label for="change-translation-app" class="">Versione App</label>
                                            <textarea id="change-translation-app" class="form-control" disabled></textarea>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                        <div class="position-relative form-group">
                                            <label for="change-translation-web" class="">Versione Web</label>
                                            <textarea id="change-translation-web" class="form-control" disabled></textarea>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="col-md-12">
                                        <button data-key="" id="translate-cancel-change" type="submit" class="btn btn-light btn-lg mr-2" {{on 'click' this.translateCancelChange}}>Annulla</button>
                                        <button data-key="" id="translate-confirm-change" data-record-id="" type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" disabled {{on 'click' this.translateComfirmChange}}>Salva</button>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    

                </div>
                {{!-- contenuto tab 2 --}}
                <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-drawer-1" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="drawer-section">
                        <p>Like Aldus PageMaker including versions of Lorem.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                {{!-- contenuto tab 3 --}}
                <div class="tab-pane" id="tab-drawer-2" role="tabpanel">
                    <div class="drawer-section">
                        <p>Lorem Ipsum has been the industry's standard dummy text ever since the 1500s.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="app-drawer-overlay d-none animated fadeIn"></div>
{{yield}}